  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Tania is a 14 years old girl born with ataxia, a motor disease, that will soon graduate from basic education after having suffered a true ordeal of school exclusion. How? Thanks to a re-entry schoolof Hogar de Cristo, where she managed to study without being discriminated. Knowing Tania, would you stop helping her? There is no greater gratification than giving and be given, because no one is too poor to not help and we need more than ever to make Chile a truly fair and dignified country for all</narrative>
